00:17:50,700 --> 00:17:52,499
(life is full of)

283
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:54,890
(new opportunities and challenges.)

284
00:17:57,500 --> 00:17:59,690
(I don't want to go on like this.)

285
00:18:00,700 --> 00:18:02,300
