00:18:10,280 --> 00:18:13,440
(Block)

287
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:27,760
(Crossroads Bar)

288
00:18:29,810 --> 00:18:31,529
Try this glass of Midsummer Fruit.

289
00:18:31,530 --> 00:18:32,890
I modified it a little.

290
00:18:40,370 --> 00:18:41,580
It's not to your taste again?

291
00:18:41,810 --> 00:18:43,089
I'm just thinking

292
00:18:43,090 --> 00:18:45,340
it's a shame this drink

293
00:18:46,430 --> 00:18:47,289
isn't the bar's signature.

294
00:18:47,290 --> 00:18:48,450
Forget about it.

295
00:18:49,260 --> 00:18:50,219
This

296
00:18:50,220 --> 00:18:51,129
may be the last drink

297
00:18:51,130 --> 00:18:52,650
I make you in this bar.

298
00:18:52,900 --> 00:18:54,130
The owner

299
00:18:54,420 --> 00:18:56,060
is selling the bar.

300
00:18:57,460 --> 00:18:59,610
I heard about it. What about you?

301
00:19:00,180 --> 00:19:01,569
What is your next step?

302
00:19:01,570 --> 00:19:03,090
My next step...

303
00:19:04,260 --> 00:19:05,569
My next step...

304
00:19:05,570 --> 00:19:08,220
is to freeload meals
off you for a while.

305
00:19:08,420 --> 00:19:09,410
Are you scared?

306
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:11,329
Sure, you can freeload meals off me.

307
00:19:11,330 --> 00:19:12,980
And I'll pay you a salary.

308
00:19:13,330 --> 00:19:15,410
Are you drunk after taking a few sips?

309
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:18,300
I'm thinking of taking over this place.

310
00:19:25,050 --> 00:19:27,540
The man downstairs walked in

311
00:19:27,940 --> 00:19:29,580
exactly the direction I wanted.

312
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:32,020
So I quit my job
and broke up with my boyfriend.

313
00:19:32,850 --> 00:19:35,170
I want to say goodbye

314
00:19:35,260 --> 00:19:36,690
and take on new opportunities.

315
00:19:38,850 --> 00:19:40,020
Let's partner up.

316
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:41,699
I'll invest, while you do the work.

317
00:19:41,700 --> 00:19:43,600
You're not trying to make me
your sugar baby, are you?

318
00:19:43,600 --> 00:19:44,419
I don't do such things.

319
00:19:44,420 --> 00:19:45,410
Get lost.

320
00:19:45,700 --> 00:19:48,090
No, didn't I just give you
a few free drinks?

321
00:19:48,260 --> 00:19:49,769
You're not really
interested in me, are you?

322
00:19:49,770 --> 00:19:51,340
I'm serious.

323
00:19:51,420 --> 00:19:52,529
Forget it if you don't want it.

324
00:19:52,530 --> 00:19:54,650
You won't have another chance like this.

325
00:19:55,050 --> 00:19:56,179
I want it.

326
00:19:56,180 --> 00:19:57,699
I can work for you.

327
00:19:57,700 --> 00:19:58,820
But

328
00:20:00,050 --> 00:20:02,019
I want to officially become
a shareholder when we make money.

329
00:20:02,020 --> 00:20:04,260
You're farsighted.

330
00:20:05,610 --> 00:20:08,170
Okay, you can do whatever you want.

331
00:20:08,850 --> 00:20:09,820
Okay.

332
00:20:09,980 --> 00:20:11,529
Let's celebrate.

333
00:20:11,530 --> 00:20:14,260
Resignation and breakup.
Two happy occasions.

334
00:20:14,570 --> 00:20:15,650
Happy?

335
00:20:15,700 --> 00:20:17,820
Fight fire with fire.
Two wrongs make one right.

336
00:20:18,610 --> 00:20:20,170
Okay. Happy.

337
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:33,720
(Crossroads)

338
00:20:35,220 --> 00:20:37,370
Let's start
by welcoming our new employees.

339
00:20:39,810 --> 00:20:40,699
I'm really glad

340
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:42,650
to have you join our team.

341
00:20:42,660 --> 00:20:43,899
I hope you can learn more

342
00:20:43,900 --> 00:20:45,659
from our old staff in the next few days.

343
00:20:45,660 --> 00:20:47,049
Whether it's the delivery speed

344
00:20:47,050 --> 00:20:48,289
or the service quality,

345
00:20:48,290 --> 00:20:50,500
I hope you'll all learn something.

346
00:20:50,570 --> 00:20:53,259
But we're not the only ones
learning from you.

347
00:20:53,260 --> 00:20:54,480
You're also learning from us.

348
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:55,899
We're gonna learn from you too, right?

349
00:20:55,900 --> 00:20:57,780
So I hope we can progress together

350
00:20:57,810 --> 00:20:59,850
and make our bar better.

351
00:21:00,220 --> 00:21:02,090
An extra portion would be good enough.

352
00:21:05,980 --> 00:21:07,219
You've been coughing for days.

353
00:21:07,220 --> 00:21:08,740
You should check it out at the hospital.

354
00:21:09,460 --> 00:21:11,129
It's okay. It just keeps recurring.

355
00:21:11,130 --> 00:21:13,020
No need to go to the hospital.

356
00:21:17,980 --> 00:21:19,580
Take a break. Take a sip of water.

357
00:21:19,810 --> 00:21:21,130
Thank you.

358
00:21:26,610 --> 00:21:28,540
You're burning.

359
00:21:28,850 --> 00:21:30,450
It's your hand that's cold.

360
00:21:31,610 --> 00:21:32,640
Have you sent the invitations?

361
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:34,780
What invitations? I'll send them
after you go to the hospital.

362
00:21:34,900 --> 00:21:36,529
No, we're about to open up for business.

363
00:21:36,530 --> 00:21:38,170
- I still have...
- Go to the hospital.

364
00:21:45,050 --> 00:21:47,220
What are you doing? Put me down.

365
00:21:47,660 --> 00:21:49,450
What are you doing?

366
00:22:19,660 --> 00:22:21,060
It's still not finished.

367
00:22:21,810 --> 00:22:22,739
What time is it?

368
00:22:22,740 --> 00:22:25,450
Stop asking. Continue sleeping.

369
00:22:28,050 --> 00:22:29,650
I feel much better already.

370
00:22:30,260 --> 00:22:31,849
Your fever is almost 40 degrees.

371
00:22:31,850 --> 00:22:33,740
Can you heal so fast?

372
00:22:44,700 --> 00:22:46,020
Look at you.

373
00:22:46,610 --> 00:22:50,130
You'll make money
but you won't be able to enjoy it.

374
00:22:52,610 --> 00:22:54,450
You don't have to challenge me.

375
00:22:55,980 --> 00:22:57,930
Since I decide to do something,

376
00:22:58,180 --> 00:23:00,090
I must do it well.

377
00:23:02,570 --> 00:23:05,019
I support you in doing it well.

378
00:23:05,020 --> 00:23:06,930
I support you to do it tomorrow.

379
00:23:07,940 --> 00:23:09,410
But tonight...

380
00:23:10,020 --> 00:23:11,300
Just tonight.

381
00:23:11,700 --> 00:23:13,890
I beg you to get some rest, okay?

382
00:23:18,500 --> 00:23:20,020
Fine.

383
00:23:29,660 --> 00:23:30,820
Go to sleep.

384
00:23:51,180 --> 00:23:53,740
How about you and I be together?

385
00:23:56,370 --> 00:23:57,820
We can eat together,

386
00:23:58,740 --> 00:24:00,930
drink together, club together,

387
00:24:01,260 --> 00:24:03,049
and do all the things we've never done.

388
00:24:03,050 --> 00:24:04,060
Okay?

389
00:24:04,810 --> 00:24:05,930
Xia Guo.

390
00:24:06,850 --> 00:24:08,540
I'm talking to you.

391
00:24:08,980 --> 00:24:11,410
Xia Guo.

392
00:24:12,420 --> 00:24:13,930
Don't pretend to sleep.

393
00:24:19,740 --> 00:24:21,170
You're pretending to sleep.

394
00:24:31,500 --> 00:24:33,699
Xia Guo's exclusive red packet
has arrived.

395
00:24:33,700 --> 00:24:35,739
I wish you all the best.

396
00:24:35,740 --> 00:24:37,580
Good luck.

397
00:24:38,090 --> 00:24:40,740
You didn't show up
for the opening the other day.

398
00:24:41,530 --> 00:24:42,529
Since you gave me

399
00:24:42,530 --> 00:24:44,060
a red packet,

400
00:24:44,090 --> 00:24:45,170
I'll forgive you.

401
00:24:45,850 --> 00:24:47,569
I really couldn't come back.

402
00:24:47,570 --> 00:24:49,049
I wanted to come.

403
00:24:49,050 --> 00:24:51,499
What's wrong? You can't act freely
after marrying into a rich family?

404
00:24:51,500 --> 00:24:53,820
Don't talk about it. It's a long story.

405
00:24:54,180 --> 00:24:56,130
Here. Please enjoy.

406
00:24:56,530 --> 00:24:58,370
- Thank you.
- Here. Try it.

407
00:25:02,850 --> 00:25:03,930
What do you think?

408
00:25:04,980 --> 00:25:06,260
The drink's good.

409
00:25:06,980 --> 00:25:08,340
The bartender's better.

410
00:25:11,850 --> 00:25:13,820
- Allen.
- Coming.

411
00:25:14,220 --> 00:25:15,450
I'll head over first.

412
00:25:15,700 --> 00:25:16,980
Have fun.

413
00:25:23,900 --> 00:25:25,939
Watch your words. You scared him.

414
00:25:25,940 --> 00:25:27,259
He's a kid.

415
00:25:27,260 --> 00:25:28,699
Kid?

416
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:30,089
He's already an adult, okay?

417
00:25:30,090 --> 00:25:32,269
And can't you tell he likes you?

418
00:25:32,269 --> 00:25:33,329
Don't you want to give it a try?

419
00:25:33,330 --> 00:25:34,179
Try?

420
00:25:34,180 --> 00:25:35,419
He's my business partner.

421
00:25:35,420 --> 00:25:37,499
So what if he's your business partner?

422
00:25:37,500 --> 00:25:39,369
Guo, look how good

423
00:25:39,370 --> 00:25:40,980
you are now.

424
00:25:41,370 --> 00:25:42,890
What happened to you and Mr. Xue?

425
00:25:42,940 --> 00:25:43,739
He went to Singapore.

426
00:25:43,740 --> 00:25:45,410
Are you sure you're not going with him?

427
00:25:46,900 --> 00:25:48,340
I wanted to go,

428
00:25:49,130 --> 00:25:50,500
but he...

429
00:25:50,570 --> 00:25:52,610
He won't let you go?

430
00:25:54,130 --> 00:25:55,450
He was hesitant.

431
00:25:56,260 --> 00:25:58,410
He just can't give me

432
00:25:58,770 --> 00:26:00,130
a clear answer.

433
00:26:00,850 --> 00:26:02,529
All I really wanted was a word from him,

434
00:26:02,530 --> 00:26:04,170
but he won't give it to me.

435
00:26:06,330 --> 00:26:09,699
Guo, why don't you start
by dating long distance?

436
00:26:09,700 --> 00:26:11,129
No.

437
00:26:11,130 --> 00:26:13,780
I can't stand the uncertainty anymore.

438
00:26:14,610 --> 00:26:16,019
When I came to Shanghai,

439
00:26:16,020 --> 00:26:18,300
I didn't think
I'll split up with Yu Jian.

440
00:26:18,660 --> 00:26:21,090
But it still happened.

441
00:26:21,850 --> 00:26:24,020
I don't want to repeat the same mistake.

442
00:26:25,810 --> 00:26:27,170
It doesn't matter, Guo.

443
00:26:27,290 --> 00:26:28,930
I figured it out anyway.

444
00:26:28,940 --> 00:26:31,569
The most important thing
is to depend on yourself.

445
00:26:31,570 --> 00:26:32,899
And you must find

446
00:26:32,900 --> 00:26:34,650
someone who really likes you.

447
00:26:34,940 --> 00:26:37,020
Look how many wrinkles I've got

448
00:26:37,260 --> 00:26:38,809
since I got married.

449
00:26:38,810 --> 00:26:40,289
I even have eyebags now.

450
00:26:40,290 --> 00:26:41,569
Thank you for your support.

451
00:26:41,570 --> 00:26:43,289
I'll drink first.
You can do whatever you want, okay?

452
00:26:43,290 --> 00:26:44,019
Okay, okay.

453
00:26:44,020 --> 00:26:45,130
Come on.

454
00:26:45,290 --> 00:26:46,370
Thank you.

455
00:26:47,420 --> 00:26:49,849
Guo, he's a good guy.

456
00:26:49,850 --> 00:26:52,740
He's motivated, hardworking,
funny and handsome.

457
00:26:53,420 --> 00:26:56,219
Most importantly,
he only has eyes for you.

458
00:26:56,220 --> 00:26:58,529
His eyes light up whenever he sees you.

459
00:26:58,530 --> 00:26:59,699
I'm so jealous.

460
00:26:59,700 --> 00:27:01,289
How can you get excited about anything?

461
00:27:01,290 --> 00:27:02,500
Of course.

462
00:27:02,700 --> 00:27:04,500
You just have to remember

463
00:27:04,530 --> 00:27:06,609
the most important thing for a woman

464
00:27:06,610 --> 00:27:09,410
is to find someone
who only love her and make her happy.

465
00:27:09,700 --> 00:27:12,769
Guo, I really hope

466
00:27:12,770 --> 00:27:13,809
you can be happy.

467
00:27:13,810 --> 00:27:15,890
So whatever choice you make,

468
00:27:16,050 --> 00:27:16,849
I'll support you.

469
00:27:16,850 --> 00:27:18,090
You have to be brave.

470
00:27:18,330 --> 00:27:19,890
Okay, be brave.

471
00:27:20,460 --> 00:27:21,500
Here. Cheers.

472
00:27:22,130 --> 00:27:23,690
Cheers.

473
00:27:50,810 --> 00:27:52,259
Are you being a free driver again?

474
00:27:52,260 --> 00:27:53,820
It's called additional service.

475
00:27:55,980 --> 00:27:57,220
Come on.

476
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:19,239
♪Our eyes met♪

477
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:23,200
♪The bridge to happiness♪

478
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:27,159
♪The world is too small♪

479
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:31,359
♪It's all your smiles♪

480
00:28:31,360 --> 00:28:36,119
♪Beating pulse♪

481
00:28:36,120 --> 00:28:40,439
♪You're the light in my eyes♪

482
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:43,560
♪Warm poetic sun♪

483
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:48,519
♪The past hidden in my heart♪

484
00:28:48,520 --> 00:28:50,399
♪Open in full bloom♪

485
00:28:50,400 --> 00:28:53,120
♪You're the light in my eyes♪

486
00:28:58,200 --> 00:29:01,240
♪My sunshine♪

487
00:29:12,850 --> 00:29:14,340
Thank you.

488
00:29:14,700 --> 00:29:15,890
Settling accounts again?

489
00:29:17,090 --> 00:29:18,129
I had a look.

490
00:29:18,130 --> 00:29:19,219
Our revenue this month

491
00:29:19,220 --> 00:29:20,610
is about what I expected.

492
00:29:20,810 --> 00:29:22,769
Isn't it New Year's and Christmas soon?

493
00:29:22,770 --> 00:29:24,370
We need to increase our budget.

494
00:29:24,500 --> 00:29:26,129
Everything is about

495
00:29:26,130 --> 00:29:28,019
vibes and sense of occasion these days.

496
00:29:28,020 --> 00:29:29,300
We can't lose.

497
00:29:29,330 --> 00:29:31,130
And we can make more money.

498
00:29:33,090 --> 00:29:35,690
I'm not that interested in making money.

499
00:29:36,610 --> 00:29:38,020
What are you interested in then?

500
00:29:39,770 --> 00:29:40,980
You.

501
00:29:43,810 --> 00:29:46,340
Didn't you hear everything
I said in the hospital?

502
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:50,240
I...

503
00:29:50,240 --> 00:29:51,799
You're pretending you can't remember,
aren't you?

504
00:29:51,799 --> 00:29:52,739
Let me say it again.

505
00:29:52,740 --> 00:29:54,060
No, no, no.

506
00:29:54,570 --> 00:29:56,220
Don't scare me.

507
00:29:56,610 --> 00:29:58,049
Don't joke like that with me.

508
00:29:58,050 --> 00:29:59,740
Joke?

509
00:30:00,260 --> 00:30:02,289
You're a woman, and I'm a man.

510
00:30:02,290 --> 00:30:04,049
We're over 18 and single.

511
00:30:04,050 --> 00:30:05,450
Why can't we be together?

512
00:30:05,460 --> 00:30:08,170
Yes, you're over 18, but...

513
00:30:10,130 --> 00:30:11,769
You're too young.

514
00:30:11,770 --> 00:30:14,129
I'm young, but you've never given it a try.

515
00:30:14,130 --> 00:30:15,820
How do you know it won't work?

516
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:17,410
I...

517
00:30:18,530 --> 00:30:20,019
Let me put it this way.

518
00:30:20,020 --> 00:30:21,340
I don't think

519
00:30:22,260 --> 00:30:24,219
I'm at my best right now.

520
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:27,329
I'm still working on a lot of things.

521
00:30:27,330 --> 00:30:30,930
I can't take action
without thinking about the consequences.

522
00:30:37,660 --> 00:30:39,419
I can't make decisions
as easily as you do.

523
00:30:39,420 --> 00:30:40,690
Do you understand?

524
00:30:40,700 --> 00:30:41,930
Decision-making again.

525
00:30:43,740 --> 00:30:45,580
Is it that hard?

526
00:30:46,770 --> 00:30:48,340
I don't know how to explain it.

527
00:30:49,370 --> 00:30:50,370
It's just that...

528
00:31:09,610 --> 00:31:10,780
Look at them.

529
00:31:11,330 --> 00:31:13,610
Look. Look at the couple over there.

530
00:31:14,530 --> 00:31:16,569
No matter what happened to them

531
00:31:16,570 --> 00:31:17,979
yesterday or tomorrow,

532
00:31:17,980 --> 00:31:20,690
they're happy today.

533
00:31:20,770 --> 00:31:21,890
Right?

534
00:31:26,500 --> 00:31:27,850
Let's make another bet.
Are you addicted?

535
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:29,899
Another bet?

536
00:31:29,900 --> 00:31:31,289
You're the one
who's afraid to make a decision.

537
00:31:31,290 --> 00:31:33,609
That's why we're leaving it to fate.
Look over there. Look.

538
00:31:33,610 --> 00:31:36,690
If the guy raises his glass first,

539
00:31:37,020 --> 00:31:38,610
you'll become my girlfriend today.

540
00:31:39,180 --> 00:31:40,849
If the girl raises her glass first,

541
00:31:40,850 --> 00:31:43,740
you're still my boss tomorrow, okay?

542
00:31:44,810 --> 00:31:45,739
Allen, this is...

543
00:31:45,740 --> 00:31:48,220
Don't interrupt. Look, look.

544
00:31:50,770 --> 00:31:52,300
Look.

545
00:32:27,090 --> 00:32:28,820
Waiter, get me the bill.

546
00:32:33,810 --> 00:32:34,739
Here's your bill.

547
00:32:34,740 --> 00:32:35,780
It's destined.

548
00:32:44,290 --> 00:32:46,569
Enough. Is making money a bad thing?

549
00:32:46,570 --> 00:32:47,930
Don't overthink it.

550
00:33:48,980 --> 00:33:50,450
Happy New Year!

551
00:33:50,740 --> 00:33:52,500
Aren't you taking
today's high-speed train home?

552
00:33:53,420 --> 00:33:54,899
It was canceled.

553
00:33:54,900 --> 00:33:56,179
I can't go home now.

554
00:33:56,180 --> 00:33:58,850
I'm here to freeload
a New Year's dinner from my boss.

555
00:33:59,020 --> 00:34:00,540
I brought things.

556
00:34:01,020 --> 00:34:02,340
